what's been--

00:15:01.760 --> 00:15:03.190
ANRICK BREGMAN: Well, it was
amazing for the team, because

00:15:03.190 --> 00:15:05.630
we had a lot of distance
between everybody.

00:15:05.630 --> 00:15:09.690
