process of choosing one of the

00:15:46.020 --> 00:15:46.920
several options.

00:15:46.920 --> 00:15:47.230
PETE LEPAGE: Right.

00:15:47.230 --> 00:15:48.790
ANRICK BREGMAN: But that makes
it a fun process rather than a

00:15:48.790 --> 00:15:49.795
very stressful one.

00:15:49.795 --> 00:15:50.220
PETE LEPAGE: Yeah.

00:15:50.220 --> 00:15:52.600
