comfortable, you can share.

00:16:21.760 --> 00:16:23.680
So that's a detail.

00:16:23.680 --> 00:16:24.480
It just makes sense.

00:16:24.480 --> 00:16:27.920
It just makes it easier and more
fun for the whole team.

